OL,3,CParking fines to go up by #25 in
OL,4,CGuernsey
OL,6,FIt will soon cost more to pay a
OL,7,Fparking fine in Guernsey.
OL,9,FThe States of Deliberation has
OL,10,Fapproved a #25 increase to fixed
OL,11,Fpenalty notices from Friday 19 July.
OL,13,FBand A tickets, usually issued for
OL,14,Foverstaying in a space, will go up
OL,15,Ffrom #40 to #65.
OL,17,FBand B tickets for offences such as
OL,18,Fdriving without a numberplate will
OL,19,Falso rise from #70 to #95.
