OL,3,CParking fines to go up by #25 in
OL,4,CGuernsey
OL,6,FThe highest level Band C fixed penalty
OL,7,Fnotices cover issues such as driving
OL,8,Fwithout a seatbelt or while using a
OL,9,Fmobile phone and will now cost
OL,10,Fmotorists #125, up from #100.
OL,12,FIf the fine is paid within seven days
OL,13,Fthen it is reduced by #10.
OL,15,FThe changes in rates are the first
OL,16,Fsince offence bands were introduced
OL,17,Fmore than a decade ago.
