OL,3,CParking fines to go up by #25 in
OL,4,CGuernsey
OL,6,FGuernsey's Home Affairs Committee
OL,7,Fchampioned the move, saying in a
OL,8,Fpolicy letter that it hopes "to
OL,9,Fmaintain a fair and proportionate
OL,10,Fpenalty, as well as provide an
OL,11,Fappropriate deterrent to those who may
OL,12,Fotherwise fail to comply".
OL,14,FThere are around 14,000 notices issued
OL,15,Fin Guernsey each year, mostly for Band
OL,16,FA issues.
OL,18,FThe increase is expected to bring in
OL,19,Fat least an extra #350,000 annually.
